items.title: Signature Chicken
items.description: A tender all-white meat chicken breast fillet, marinated in an authentic blend of Louisiana seasonings, then hand battered and breaded in our all new buttermilk coating. Served with crisp barrel cured pickles and Classic or Spicy Mayonnaise, served on a warm and toasted buttery brioche bun.

items.title: Boneless
items.description: Seven juicy all white meat boneless wings. Round it out with one of our signature sides and a hot buttery biscuit.

items.title: Tenders
